==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Enrange
<hw>En*range"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>en-</ets> + <ets>range</ets>. Cf. <er>Enrank</er>,
<er>Arrange</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>To range in order; to put in
rank; to arrange.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To rove over; to range.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Spenser.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Enrank</ent>⟦br⟧
